snippet.title: "Project Runway" Wii - Trailer
snippet.description: Join Heidi, Tim, Nina, and Michael as you face exciting fashion challenges in "Project Runway" the video game from Atari. Featuring the contestants from Season 6.  Out March 2, 2010 for the Nintendo Wii.
